							<p class="lead text-primary">Edgewater Live was formed in 2011 with a desire to
								bring accessible, danceable, good-time music from many genres to
								venues and private parties throughout the Denver Metro area, I-70
								corridor and beyond.</p>

							<p>Made up of long time veterans of the Denver music scene and led
								by vocalist James Elias, Edgewater Live seeks to meet the needs of
								our clients by tailoring our extensive, varied playlist to fit the
								occasion perfectly. With a two-guitar attack and a grooving rhythm
								section, Edgewater Live engages the crowd to sing and dance along to
								familiar hit songs from the past and present.</p>

